"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-olympian-hamal-releases-autobiography\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, Sept 20: Olympian Surendra Bahadaur Hamal has launched his autobiography \\\"Olympian\\\" at National Sports Council, Tripureshwor in the Capital City on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999975218543, \"rank\": 2.4707853943948696e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surendra_Bikram_Shah\", \"score\": 0.9999895313831069, \"rank\": 1.0468726581220664e-05, \"text\": \"Surendra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surendra_Bikram_Shah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surendra_Bikram_Shah\"}, {\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hamal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999975218543, \"rank\": 2.4707853943948696e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999320805594981, \"rank\": 6.792404742258995e-05, \"text\": \"National Sports Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tripureshwor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tripureshwor\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tripureshwor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tripureshwor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The book\\u00a0was jointly lauched\\u00a0by the Olympians\\u00a0-\\u00a0Anita Maharjan (Shooting), Pushpa Ojha (Athletics), Sangina Baidhya (Taekwondo), Jangdish Pradhan (Weightlifting) and Hamal himself.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharjan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maharjan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharjan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharjan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympian\\\"-the first autobiography of a Nepali\\u00a0sportsmen, is an inspirational book especially for aspiring Nepali players.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.999999993700385, \"rank\": 6.288528581700042e-09, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.999999993700385, \"rank\": 6.288528581700042e-09, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the book, Hamal, as a storyteller, has beautifully shared his passionate sports journey along with the challenges he had encountered while achieving his dreams.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hamal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the function, Hamal shared his short life stories that he had missed in the book.Various members of the Olympic Committee also accompanied the session.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Including various national sports events, Hamal has also represented Nepal in South Asian Games (SAG), Olympics\\u00a0and other international sports events in the weightlifting category.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hamal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamal\"}, {\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.451548551933198e-19, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamal is also Nepal's first weightlifting medalist.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.451548551933198e-19, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ballot Box Revolt: What RSP's breakthrough victory...\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\", \"score\": 0.76029011953709, \"rank\": 0.3152706813734456, \"text\": \"RSP\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Warning, Threat or Opportunity?\", \"from\"